data.chText: （大学教师带领学生作专题讨论的）研讨课
data.enText: a class at a university or college when a small group of students and a teacher discuss or study a particular topic

data.chText: 教学形式为讲座和研讨课。
data.enText: Teaching is by lectures and seminars.
a meeting for discussion or training

data.chText: 为期一天的管理研讨会

means: (大学教师带领学生作专题讨论的)研讨课

tr: a course offered for a small group of advanced students
any meeting for an exchange of ideas

value.def: A seminar is a meeting where a group of people discuss a problem or topic.

example.ex: ...a series of half-day seminars to help businessmen get the best value from investing in information technology.
example.tran: 旨在帮助商界人士从投资信息技术中获得最大价值的一系列半日研讨会

value.def: A seminar is a class at a college or university in which the teacher and a small group of students discuss a topic.

example.ex: Students are asked to prepare material in advance of each weekly seminar.
example.tran: 学生要在上每星期的研讨课前备好材料。

value.tran: (大学里由教师指导一小组学生参加的)研讨班，研讨课
